all that Japanese food

11:07.323 --> 11:09.753
on that menu when you're not trained,

11:09.753 --> 11:10.827
it doesn't quite make sense.

11:10.827 --> 11:12.641
(upbeat dramatic music)

11:12.641 --> 11:15.665
- [Sukie] Oh my goodness,
this is not good.

11:15.665 --> 11:17.531
- There's not a lot of
people in Starkville

11:17.531 --> 11:19.502
that like our sushi, it's
a little bit different

11:19.502 --> 11:22.018
from what other places in Starkville have.

11:23.430 --> 11:26.067
(upbeat dramatic music)

11:26.067 --> 11:26.935
- Oh.

11:29.271 --> 11:31.009
- God, they're slow.

11:35.174 --> 11:37.270
- Sukie runs her kitchen
the way she wants to.

11:37.270 --> 11:40.711
It always takes too
long in-between tickets,

11:40.711 --> 11:43.568
but there is really
nothing I can do about it.

11:43.568 --> 11:45.194
- This food is taking way too long,

11:45.194 --> 11:47.190
I've been waiting over
an hour for raw fish!

11:47.190 --> 11:49.740
(dramatic music)

11:49.740 --> 11:51.722
Oh, my God, I can't take this anymore.

11:53.669 --> 11:54.538
Ah, God!

11:54.538 --> 11:58.013
(upbeat dramatic music)

11:59.698 --> 12:01.349
- [Lindsey] Dammit.

